objenome.util.bean

Class ProxyInvocationHandler

  • java.lang.Object
    • objenome.util.bean.ProxyInvocationHandler
  • All Implemented Interfaces:
    java.io.Serializable, java.lang.Cloneable, java.lang.reflect.InvocationHandler
    Direct Known Subclasses:
    ProxyInvocationHandlerPropertyChangeSupport

    public class ProxyInvocationHandler
extends java.lang.Object
implements java.lang.reflect.InvocationHandler, java.io.Serializable, java.lang.Cloneable
    Serializable InvocationHandler for data holding classes. All attributes are accessible via the normal bean getters and setters (get/set/has/is). Furthermore the methods hashCode, equals, toString and clone are implemented.
    Author:
    Joachim Baumann, Peter Fichtner
